<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 10:07:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队证实，周二，十名以色列国防军士兵在加沙的不同事件中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/nine-idf-soldiers-killed-in-separate-gaza-incidents-on-tuesday-israeli-army-confirms/0000018b-89ba-dd28-a7df-99bf51f70000</link><description>周二在加沙地带被杀的以色列士兵总数增至12人。以色列国防军周二在加沙地带北部贾巴利亚难民营的行动控制了哈马斯军事据点，并杀死了哈马斯贾巴利亚旅指挥官</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 08:23:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/nine-idf-soldiers-killed-in-separate-gaza-incidents-on-tuesday-israeli-army-confirms/0000018b-89ba-dd28-a7df-99bf51f70000</guid></item><item><title>十名以色列士兵在加沙地面行动中丧生；以色列加强红海部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article-live/11-israeli-soldiers-killed-as-idf-expands-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-8925-d055-afbf-bba702e90000</link><description>周二，10 名以色列士兵在加沙地面行动中丧生，使加沙地带的以色列死亡人数达到 12 人 ■ 在也门胡塞武装发动远程导弹和无人机袭击后，以色列军舰部署在红海作为增援部队 ■ 以色列空袭导致易卜拉欣·比亚里 (Ibrahim Biari) 身亡哈马斯贾巴利亚旅指挥官，也是 10 月 7 日大屠杀的领导人之一 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部报告称，有 8,000 多名巴勒斯坦人被杀 ■ 加沙被扣押的人质人数为 240 人，其中 40 人仍然失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀中丧生的士兵</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 05:19:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article-live/11-israeli-soldiers-killed-as-idf-expands-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-8925-d055-afbf-bba702e90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙的推进速度超预期使其任务变得更加复杂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-armys-rapid-advance-in-gaza-makes-soldiers-mission-even-more-complex/0000018b-878e-d055-afbf-b7af50c00000</link><description>以色列军队深入加沙地带的影响只会随着时间的推移而显现出来，因为伊朗越来越担心哈马斯的抵御能力。与此同时，美国在加沙准备了数月后，倾向于采取精确、有针对性的打击战略</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 04:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-armys-rapid-advance-in-gaza-makes-soldiers-mission-even-more-complex/0000018b-878e-d055-afbf-b7af50c00000</guid></item><item><title>玻利维亚因加沙问题与以色列断绝关系，其他拉美国家召回特使</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/bolivia-severs-ties-with-israel-over-gaza-other-latin-american-countries-recall-envoys/0000018b-88b4-df47-a3df-febdc61f0001</link><description>三个南美国家谴责以色列对加沙的袭击，并谴责巴勒斯坦公民的死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 02:39:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/bolivia-severs-ties-with-israel-over-gaza-other-latin-american-countries-recall-envoys/0000018b-88b4-df47-a3df-febdc61f0001</guid></item><item><title>直接火箭弹袭击，部分保护：以色列遭受轰炸最严重的城市的医院如何运作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/hospital-serving-israels-most-bombarded-city-operating-at-30-percent-capacity/0000018b-8887-dd28-a7df-9897d1dd0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，阿什凯隆的巴尔兹莱医院已经遭受了三次直接火箭弹袭击。尽管其位置不稳定，但仅受到部分保护，因此，尽管需求和必要性很高，但其入住率仍仅为 30%</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 02:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/hospital-serving-israels-most-bombarded-city-operating-at-30-percent-capacity/0000018b-8887-dd28-a7df-9897d1dd0000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在加沙地面行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-8859-df47-a3df-fe592d370000</link><description>阵亡的士兵被命名为参谋军士。来自拉马特甘的 Roei Wolf 和参谋军士。莫迪因的拉维·利普希茨</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 01:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-8859-df47-a3df-fe592d370000</guid></item><item><title>为了保持世界支持，以色列加大对加沙的人道主义援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/to-retain-world-support-israel-plays-up-humanitarian-aid-to-gaza/0000018b-875e-d055-afbf-b7ffa0bb0000</link><description>过去几天，以色列对向加沙地带运送食品、水和医疗用品的公开立场发生了重大变化，因为人们认识到对这一行动的批评只会越来越多。现在的目标：区分人道主义援助和燃料的入境</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 00:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/to-retain-world-support-israel-plays-up-humanitarian-aid-to-gaza/0000018b-875e-d055-afbf-b7ffa0bb0000</guid></item><item><title>康奈尔大学学生因针对犹太学生的死亡威胁被捕，面临联邦指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/person-of-interest-held-in-connection-to-death-threats-against-jewish-cornell-students/0000018b-8824-dd28-a7df-983591a60000</link><description>周日晚上，常春藤联盟学校的犹太学生被要求锁在自己的房间里，因为有人呼吁杀害和强奸“所有犹太妇女”</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 00:17:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/person-of-interest-held-in-connection-to-death-threats-against-jewish-cornell-students/0000018b-8824-dd28-a7df-983591a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列联合国特使的廉价挑衅</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/cheap-provocation-from-israels-united-nations-envoy/0000018b-8779-d055-afbf-b7fb429f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 22:18:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/cheap-provocation-from-israels-united-nations-envoy/0000018b-8779-d055-afbf-b7fb429f0000</guid></item><item><title>击败哈马斯后，以色列必须与拉马拉对话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/after-defeating-hamas-israel-must-seek-dialogue-with-ramallah/0000018b-8758-d805-a98f-b7d94df60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 22:09:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/after-defeating-hamas-israel-must-seek-dialogue-with-ramallah/0000018b-8758-d805-a98f-b7d94df60000</guid></item><item><title>现在是以色列袭击伊朗的最佳时机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/there-will-never-be-a-better-time-for-israel-to-strike-in-iran/0000018b-8758-df47-a3df-ff592b2b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 22:06:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/there-will-never-be-a-better-time-for-israel-to-strike-in-iran/0000018b-8758-df47-a3df-ff592b2b0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-31/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-87b5-df47-a3df-ffbdcaee0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 21:53:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-31/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-87b5-df47-a3df-ffbdcaee0000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查发现，右翼以色列人在战时决策方面更信任军事指挥官而不是内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/poll-finds-right-wing-israelis-trust-military-commanders-over-netanyahu/0000018b-8646-df47-a3df-fe4fbef00000</link><description>该民意调查还审查了公众对可能释放巴勒斯坦囚犯以换取哈马斯释放以色列人质的看法，以及对 10 月 7 日失败进行公开调查的首选时间</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 20:16:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/poll-finds-right-wing-israelis-trust-military-commanders-over-netanyahu/0000018b-8646-df47-a3df-fe4fbef00000</guid></item><item><title>“强奸和谋杀没有正当理由”：哥伦比亚大学教师回应同僚宽恕哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/no-justification-for-rape-and-murder-columbia-faculty-respond-to-peers-condoning-hamas/0000018b-86e8-df47-a3df-fee9d0dd0000</link><description>犹太学生人数较多的哥伦比亚大学成为10月7日以来美国校园爆发摩擦的关键战场</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 19:49:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/no-justification-for-rape-and-murder-columbia-faculty-respond-to-peers-condoning-hamas/0000018b-86e8-df47-a3df-fee9d0dd0000</guid></item><item><title>杰克·卢确认担任下一任美国驻以色列大使</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/jack-lew-confirmed-as-next-u-s-ambassador-to-israel/0000018b-8725-df47-a3df-ff2dcc030000</link><description>卢是一位 67 岁的东正教犹太裔纽约人，在很多方面都是公共服务领域中虔诚的犹太人的先驱，他强调了自己的犹太教以及与以色列的个人联系——无论是总体联系还是与 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击有关的联系</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 19:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/jack-lew-confirmed-as-next-u-s-ambassador-to-israel/0000018b-8725-df47-a3df-ff2dcc030000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列不应该将哈马斯与纳粹进行比较</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/why-israel-should-not-compare-hamas-to-the-nazis/0000018b-8692-d055-afbf-b6b34f9e0000</link><description>以色列驻联合国特使戴上黄星，既是对大屠杀幸存者和受害者的无端冒犯，又否认大屠杀与以色列对哈马斯的战争之间最根本的区别</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 18:48:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/why-israel-should-not-compare-hamas-to-the-nazis/0000018b-8692-d055-afbf-b6b34f9e0000</guid></item><item><title>“美国校园里的一些学生认为所有以色列人都是殖民者，所以屠杀他们是可以的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-31/ty-article-podcast/some-students-think-all-israelis-are-colonizers-so-its-okay-to-slaughter-them/0000018b-8627-d055-afbf-b6a72afd0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 18:46:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-31/ty-article-podcast/some-students-think-all-israelis-are-colonizers-so-its-okay-to-slaughter-them/0000018b-8627-d055-afbf-b6a72afd0000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查发现，拜登因支持以色列而失去了阿拉伯裔美国人的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/biden-bleeding-support-from-arab-americans-over-his-support-for-israel-poll-finds/0000018b-869a-d055-afbf-b6bb82e20000</link><description>尽管估计只有 345 万穆斯林生活在美国，仅占该国总人口的 1% 多一点，但这些社区都集中在选举地图上的关键州</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 17:54:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/biden-bleeding-support-from-arab-americans-over-his-support-for-israel-poll-finds/0000018b-869a-d055-afbf-b6bb82e20000</guid></item><item><title>当局担心哈马斯袭击后许多以色列人的命运仍不明朗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/authorities-fear-the-fate-of-many-israelis-will-remain-unknown-following-hamas-attack/0000018b-865f-d055-afbf-b6ff26380000</link><description>迄今为止，在以色列国防军和以色列警方以及阿布卡比尔法医研究所和舒拉军事设施的其他调查和医疗小组的努力下，已确认了 1,135 名平民和士兵的身份。</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 17:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/authorities-fear-the-fate-of-many-israelis-will-remain-unknown-following-hamas-attack/0000018b-865f-d055-afbf-b6ff26380000</guid></item><item><title>因埃尔多安的愤怒，以色列超市停止从土耳其进口</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/irked-by-erdogan-israeli-supermarkets-halt-imports-from-turkey/0000018b-866e-dd28-a7df-967f57360000</link><description>两国之间的经济关系蓬勃发展，但在埃尔多安的强硬讲话后，以色列人对土耳其西红柿的厌恶可能是贸易进一步削弱的先兆</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 17:18:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/irked-by-erdogan-israeli-supermarkets-halt-imports-from-turkey/0000018b-866e-dd28-a7df-967f57360000</guid></item></channel></rss>